Entity Space

Event create_space
  EventInput
    name          string        required
    icon          string        optional
    color         string        optional
    description   string        optional

Event update_space
  EventInput
    space_id      UUID          required
    name          string        optional
    icon          string        optional
    color         string        optional
    description   string        optional

Event archive_space
  EventInput
    space_id      UUID          required

Event search_space
  EventInput
    space_id      UUID          required
    query         string        required — full-text search term
    entity_types  string[]      optional — filter by entity type (Task, Note, Activity, etc.)
                                defaults to all entity types
